---
summary: I can kick someone with a higher power level than my own (and other powerlevel confusion)
---
created: 2014-12-05 13:48:28.0
creator: joachim
description: |-
  If my power level allows me to kick/ban, I can do it to someone whose power level is higher.
  Not intended apparently
